/>\n依個世界想唔做錯，唯一既方法就係乜都唔做。<br />\n試完錯完，再努力諗辦法，人類就係咁樣進化。<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位抽空睇完。//"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:45:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"98e2c31de3a3f22db5d27b2f344383052048f36e","tid":1972747,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"唔好鬥黃 各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb9613c1667db8712d1c363873630a9e0c2a8cc","tid":1972747,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64293a419559fd5fc4e7e0a21317ff3d8e466b90","tid":1972747,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b303ced7dab7b8273fd9a6d1311d5dd221f6aae","tid":1972747,"uid":175731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e1d7511ce370e5d8528ac3daacbadeb571c2be1b","tid":1972747,"uid":165750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7f05c6a64bc3dbacb5566648535988555d8f47","tid":1972747,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"152b6741ab30a4849d64cb2b9166e1cec2cc8cd2","tid":1972747,"uid":126626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T17:14:54.000Z","msg":"幫推，唔好內鬥！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"其實從來無內鬥<br />\n去fb搵真人傾下<br />\n就知全部係5毛搞分化<br />\n真人黃圈無人會搞挑剔"},{"pid":"1a9360a05f571cad3dcfe9c178edba7d0ccc6e8f","tid":1972747,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:15:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5d9e9a72b9a1d79bda5ad09448471f63b341948","tid":1972747,"uid":76403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28a1f029c76a08e7c10afa12266006a